videos.headline: McFarland scores first TD as a Terrapin
videos.description: RB Anthony McFarland takes off to score a 26-yard touchdown, putting Maryland up 7-0 over Minnesota.

videos.headline: Johnson runs for 81-yard TD
videos.description: Maryland's Ty Johnson turns on the afterburners to score an 81-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Turner scores first career TD for Maryland
videos.description: Kasim Hill is hit but connects with DJ Turner, who escapes the defense and high-steps his way to a 54-yard touchdown for Maryland.

videos.headline: Annexstad throws 17-yard TD pass to Bateman
videos.description: Minnesota's Zack Annexstad connects with a leaping Rashod Bateman for a 17-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Annextad INT leads to another Maryland TD
videos.description: Zack Annextad is picked off for the second time and Maryland's Tre Watson returns it 36 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Minnesota's Annexstad throws second INT of the day
videos.description: Zack Annexstad is picked off by Maryland's RaVon Davis for the touchback.

videos.headline: Okonkwo runs 21 yards for another Maryland TD
videos.description: Maryland's Chigoziem Okonkwo tiptoes the sideline as he runs 21 yards for another Terrapin touchdown.
